{"type": "article", "id": 27244, "title": "Balmain创意总监和耐克合作系列长这样 ，以及，i-D杂志有了日文版｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-05-24T10:25:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14244, "name": "浮华日报"}, {"id": 28053, "name": "Lane Crawford"}, {"id": 28060, "name": "日本护照"}, {"id": 3134, "name": "Versace"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 10699, "name": "L Brands"}, {"id": 20337, "name": "连卡佛"}, {"id": 10733, "name": "i-D"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 28062, "name": "Theory"}, {"id": 21654, "name": "Lily-Rose Depp"}, {"id": 766, "name": "香奈儿"}, {"id": 28063, "name": "Olivier Rousteing 和 NikeLab"}, {"id": 3017, "name": "Jean Paul Gaultier"}, {"id": 28064, "name": "葛饰北斋"}, {"id": 28065, "name": "Master & Dynamic"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702103310rCjlw6aIO5Ysp4UP.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/people/abercrombie-fitch-names-new-presidents-10435379/\">Abercrombie &amp; Fitch 任命两名新品牌总裁</a> ｜A&amp; F 找来了曾在 Target 百货负责时装、配饰和童装的副总裁 Stacia Andersen 担任 Abercrombie &amp; Fitch 和abercrombie kids 的品牌总裁，还有曾负责 Victoria’s Secret 销售总经理兼执行副总裁 Kristin Scott 担任 Hollister Co. 的品牌总裁。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.wsj.com/articles/versace-appoint-jonathan-akeroyd-as-chief-executive-1464011305\">Versace 换 CEO</a>｜Versace 的首席执行官 Gian Giacomo Ferraris 宣布离职，Alexander McQueen 的前 CEO Jonathan Akeroyd 6 月接任。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/lvmhs-journees-particulieres-draws-145000-visitors-10435365/\">LVMH 集团第三届公众日 Journées Particulières 很受欢迎 </a>｜公众日为期三天，从 5 月 20 日—22 日，吸引了 14.5 万人参观。LVMH 集团开放了其在法国、意大利、西班牙和瑞士等多国的香水工厂、葡萄园、皮革工厂等，让公众有机会看一看平日在店内售卖的奢侈品是怎么炼成的。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"L%20Brands%20%E7%BB%99%20Victoria%E2%80%99s%20Secret%20%E6%89%BE%E6%9D%A5%E4%BA%86%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84CEO\">L Brands 给 Victoria’s Secret 找来了新的 CEO </a>｜Jan Singer 将会在 9 月上任，将会调整 Victoria’s Secret 的生意架构，裁员 200 人。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/lane-crawford-luxe-guides-offer-themed-trips-10435307/\">香港连卡佛推出了奢华主题旅行服务</a> ｜包括“Fashion in New York,” “Culture in Paris,” “Wellness in Los Angeles,” “Design in Tokyo” and “Culinary Delights in Bangkok.” 五个主题，消费者可以通过太古旅游公司进行预订。现在连卡佛已经在店内推销这个旅行服务。在这些旅程中，连卡佛也将给出城市旅游指南信息，还有可供购物的推荐。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/i-d-launches-japanese-edition-10435291/\">i-D 杂志有了日文版，</a>第一期封面是水原希子。日文版 i-D 是半年刊，是 i-D 全球范围做的第 11 个版本，但在亚洲是先例，之前还有法文版、意大利版、澳大利亚版。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103258ZuVhLr02kyS9pqWo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/uniqlo-theory-team-up-on-shirts-10435296/\">优衣库和 Theory 推出联名男装胶囊系列，</a>主要是 T 恤和 polo 衫。将会在优衣库的部分精选门店售出，也能在优衣库的官网买到，价格在 256 美元——385 美元之间。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103259SBmdwW28uUzapiLo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103259y9Q57h04mJTOuNlV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.338\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/05/lily-rose-depp-chanel-no5-leau\">Lily-Rose Depp 成为了香奈儿香水代言人。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103300NnR4z6jYEaTipu38.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98664441\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103300blfi0LoQ7WjwyeDE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93656093\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://i-d.vice.com/en_gb/article/olivier-rousteing-has-the-midas-touch\">Olivier Rousteing 和 NikeLab 合作的系列长这样。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103300m1y5z0tFcvX6rlhe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71501272\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021033010yhCbViNQsXxuTKD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3346056\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210330132UgvyKSWMAGqcsV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3552381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103302Gw2i3c7bDBRvOSPq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103302BcHjKaRTpntEqZ6z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103303EVFcuyxdRl1DtSkZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021033033nicesI4BrO0yD5K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021033042Anjokz1u64dfLlZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103304cCuFSN7kOgIjzsdT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://sstylemagazine.com/beauty/jean-paul-gaultier-fragrance-05177022\">Jean Paul Gaultier </a>推出了卡通香水，分别以Betty Boop 为主題的女性香水 Classique 和以 Popeye 为主題的男士香水 Le Mâle。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021033041AUgbMz3ty2owev8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103305yL0hXVwmbzsMKlSW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">来看一本有趣的护照。因为 2020 年日本东京奥运会的影响，<a href=\"http://en.rocketnews24.com/2016/05/20/japans-new-ukiyo-e-passports-are-going-to-look-awesome/\">日本将重新设计严肃的护照。</a>新护照将把日本江户时代浮世绘画家葛饰北斋的经典作品《富岳三十六景》放在内页设计中。新护照将于 2019 年开始发行。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103305Mqe84Wz5LcFuNp32.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103306jFBJoYPV5MfnhDRN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021033066dQv3tZ4PYq1nmWo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70636215\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103307oiOPrpnEyKfHBSZa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">为了庆祝成立两周年，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/fashion\">美国耳机品牌 Master &amp; Dynamic 旗下的耳机款式 MH40、MH30 和 MW60 推出了 4 种全新配色，耳垫由羊皮制作。</a>耳垫的售价在 35 美元——39 美元之间。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103307whkuSEKRvZ3U9xPG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103308fHOvIkAJlF3PpGU6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103308O2Lds7SUvRzFxpQ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103309Kp9mEsdGfVieZR0k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103309hT4SxDYm3bcqynGF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}